s=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 0</strong>: The starting point of your nightmare. Navigate through the dimly lit, yellow-tinted hallways filled with old, musty carpets and flickering fluorescent lights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 0.2</strong>: A darker, more treacherous variation of Level 0. The paths are narrower, and the environment is even more disorienting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 1</strong>: Transition to a slightly more industrial setting with concrete walls and parking.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 2</strong>: A sprawling maze of dark, damp tunnels and echoing footsteps. The claustrophobic environment tests your endurance as you navigate through pipes and avoid hazardous obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 3</strong>: A chaotic blend of industrial and organic elements, with machinery intertwined with strange, pulsating growths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 4</strong>: An expansive, decrepit office space filled with endless rows of cubicles and malfunctioning electronics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 0?</strong>: A surreal, overgrown version of Level 0, where vegetation has taken over the familiar hallways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 5</strong>: The Abandoned Hotel. An eerie, deserted hotel with shifting, dimly lit corridors and ghostly apparitions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 37 (Poolrooms)</strong> : An expansive complex of interconnected rooms and corridors slightly submerged in undulating, lukewarm water.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 10</strong> : The Infinite Fields. An endless expanse of overgrown wheat fields under a perpetually overcast sky.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ocean Poolrooms </strong>: A submerged island of interconnected, flooded rooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 389 </strong>: The Gaming Hall, It resides under the complete control of The G̵̷̶̢͕̖̝̼͍͉̫̮͔̜̣̟̩̠̼̙̱̟̦̾̂̈̂ͭ͐̽͐̐͊̈̍͘̚͠͞a̱͎̤̋̔̈̈m̛̳̰͇͂ͬ̍ͩ̋̍ę͕̝̰̹ͬͤ̑͝ͅ M̶̨̧̮̻͇̮̼̠̹̝͍̒ͮ́̈͆ͪͧͭa̷͙͓̣̓͒ͫ͆͗̕͜s̖̪͔̫̼̪̾̆t̸̨̮̪̤̣̝̾͋̋̈͑̔̊̚̕͡è̶̴̛͖̼̝̪̤̖͔͓̼̻̏ͮͭ̈͒ͯͨ͆ͭ̄̍͋͛̈ͬ̚̚͟r̴̴̵̛̝̺̣̖͈͎͚̻̻̖̦͖̖̩̺̩̬ͨ̊̓̽̂̀̾̃ͧ͌̅̆̏͘͞ͅ.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 148 :</strong> An infinite, serene garden bathed in soft sunlight, with neatly trimmed hedges and vibrant flowers</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Fun</strong> <strong>:</strong> Colorful rooms resembling a child’s birthday party, filled with balloons and eerie laughter. The grinning Partygoers are always watching. Don’t join the fun.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level 404 : </strong>A broken space where reality corrupts, filled with distorted walls, floating textures, and endless visual errors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Neon Poolrooms :</strong> A surreal network of pools illuminated by fluorescent neon lights, where the water shimmers with an eerie glow and shadows seem to dance to the rhythm of an inaudible melody.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Old Memories:</strong> A world frozen in pixelated nostalgia, where strangely familiar landscapes stretch endlessly.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive the <strong>Unseen</strong>: The Backrooms are home to <strong>unknown entities</strong> and <strong>phenomena</strong>. Stay alert, stay <strong>quiet</strong>, and most importantly, <strong>stay alive</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429990/extras/f6827864544739152ba8aa2c087ae123.poster.avif?t=1742670107\" width=480 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429990/extras/f6827864544739152ba8aa2c087ae123.webm?t=1742670107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429990/extras/f6827864544739152ba8aa2c087ae123.mp4?t=1742670107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
